  <description><![CDATA[<p>Nestled in the historic centre of Gressoney La Trinité the Hotel Lo Scoiattolo is a charming and well run family hotel. The team at the Scoiattolo are dedicated to creating a relaxed atmosphere with tentative service. Dinning at the hotel is a highlight of the day in the cosy wooden clad restaurant, where typical regional dishes are served along with good quality local wine. To help you relax and rejuvenate you can use the facilities in the small spa, which are especially enticing after a day walking in the mountains.</p>]]></description>
